Uses of Interface
org.paukov.combinatorics.ICombinatoricsVector

  • Packages that use ICombinatoricsVector 
    Package Description
    org.paukov.combinatorics
    This package contains common classes and interfaces of the library such as ICombinatoricsVector, Generator and Factory.
    org.paukov.combinatorics.combination.multi
    This package contains the multicombinations generator (combinations with repetitions).
    org.paukov.combinatorics.combination.simple
    This package contains the simple combinations generator.
    org.paukov.combinatorics.composition
    This package contains the integer composition generators.
    org.paukov.combinatorics.partition
    This package contains the integer partitions generator.
    org.paukov.combinatorics.permutations
    This package contains the generators for the permutations with and without repetitions.
    org.paukov.combinatorics.subsets
    This package contains the subsets generators.
    org.paukov.combinatorics.util
    This package contains the utility classes and tools.
